      "writtenOn": "2017-12-08T22:57:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "additions, updates, and removals can\u0027t be maps because the order we handle them would be non-deterministic. Since they need to be slices for deterministic iteration, we need a way to encapsulate both the config.DatacenterConfig part and the ID part, which is why I created this struct.",
      "parentUuid": "7856c9cf_19a33746",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 28,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 32,
        "endChar": 1
      },
      "revId": "25d04572234dd3648bb1438f0754e6791298ca80",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
